
  Ralts    Psychic Type Pokémon

  RALTS senses the emotions of 
  people using the horns on its 
  head.  Ralts rarely appears 
  before people.  But when it does, 
  it draws closer if it senses 
  that the person has a positive 
  disposition. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Ralts ► Kirlia ► Gardevoir

